c_i
\sum c_i=1
\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{c_i^2}{i}
S = c(1)^2/1 + c(2)^2/2 + ...+ c(n)^2/n \geq (c(1)+..+ c(n))^2/(1+2+..+n) = 1/(n(n+1)/2) = 2/(n(n+1))
\min S = 2/(n(n+1))
c_i
1\le i \le n 
Λ(c,λ)
0
c_i
Λ(c,λ)=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\frac{c_i^2}{i}+λ\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}c_i-1\right)
\frac{\partialΛ}{\partial c_i}=\frac{2}{i}c_i+λ
c_i=-\frac{λi}{2}
\frac{\partialΛ}{\partial λ}=\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}c_i-1\right)
0=\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}c_i-1\right)=\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}-\frac{λi}{2}-1\right)=\left(-\frac{λ}{2}\sum_{i=1}^{n}i-1\right)=-\frac{λ}{2}\frac{n(n+1)}{2}-1
λ=-\frac{4}{n(n+1)}
c_i=-\frac{\frac{4}{n(n+1)}i}{2}=-\frac{2}{n(n+1)}i
\sum_{i=1}^{n}\frac{c_i^2}{i}=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\frac{\left(-\frac{2}{n(n+1)}i\right)^2}{i}=\frac{4}{\left(n(n+1)\right)^2}=\sum_{i=1}^{n}i=\frac{4}{\left(n(n+1)\right)^2}\frac{n(n+1)}{2}=\frac{2}{n(n+1)}
